##     union
tweet$comments=sapply(tweet$clean_text,remove.chars,n=1,"the|—|and|-")
tweet$comments<- gsub("(RT|via)((?:\\b\\W*@\\w+)+)","",tweet$comments)
tweet$comments<- gsub("http[^[:blank:]]+","", tweet$comments)
tweet$comments<- gsub("@\\w+", "", tweet$comments)
tweet$comments<- gsub("\\s\and", "", tweet$comments)
tweet$comments<- gsub("\\s\the", "", tweet$comments)
tweet$comments<- gsub("[ t]{2,}","", tweet$comments)
tweet$comments<- gsub("^\\s+|\\s+$","", tweet$comments)
tweet$comments<- gsub("\\d+","", tweet$comments)
tweet$comments<- gsub("[[:punct:]]","", tweet$comments)
traincorpus = Corpus(VectorSource(tweet$comments[1:10000]))
traincorpus = tm_map(traincorpus,removePunctuation)
traincorpus = tm_map(traincorpus,stripWhitespace)
traincorpus = tm_map(traincorpus,tolower)
tdmtrain = DocumentTermMatrix(traincorpus)
term_tfidf1 <- tapply(tdmtrain$v/row_sums(tdmtrain)[tdmtrain$i], tdmtrain$j, mean) * log2(nDocs(tdmtrain)/col_sums(tdmtrain > 0))
tdmtrain <- tdmtrain[,term_tfidf1 >= 0.1]
tdmtrain <- tdmtrain[row_sums(tdmtrain) > 0,]
testcorpus = Corpus(VectorSource(tweet$comments[10000:15000]))
testcorpus = tm_map(testcorpus,removePunctuation)
testcorpus = tm_map(testcorpus,stripWhitespace)
testcorpus = tm_map(testcorpus,tolower)
tdmtest = DocumentTermMatrix(testcorpus)
term_tfidf2 <- tapply(tdmtest$v/row_sums(tdmtest)[tdmtest$i], tdmtest$j, mean) * log2(nDocs(tdmtest)/col_sums(tdmtest > 0))
tdmtest <- tdmtest[,term_tfidf2 >= 0.1]
tdmtest <- tdmtest[row_sums(tdmtest) > 0,]

t1<-colnames(tdmtrain);t2<-colnames(tdmtest)
table(t1 %in% t2);length(table(c(t1,t2)))

####困惑度的计算perplexity越小说明unsupervised learning 效果越好
train_perp=ldas$train_perp[2:15]
test_perp=ldas$test_perp[2:15]
loglik=ldas$loglik
est=data.frame(x=c(2:15,2:15),
               y=c(test_perp,train_perp),
               type=c(rep('test_perplexity',14),
                      rep('train_perplexity',14) ))
ggplot(est, aes(x, y, color=type)) + 
  geom_line() + geom_point()+ 
  facet_wrap(~ type, ncol=2)+
  labs(list(title ='', x = "number of topic", y = "perplexity"))

####熵计算
alpha=sapply(ldas[[1]], slot, "alpha")
entropy=sapply(ldas[[1]], function(x) mean(apply(posterior(x)$topics, 1, 
                                                 function(z) - sum(z * log(z)))))
ae=data.frame(x=c(2:15,2:15),y=c(alpha,entropy),
              type=c(rep('alpha',14),rep('entropy',14)))
ggplot(ae, aes(x, y, color=type)) + 
  geom_line() + geom_point()+ 
  facet_wrap(~ type, ncol=2)+
  labs(list(title ='', x = "number of topic", y = "alpha and entropy"))

model=ldas$model[[10]]
train_topic<-posterior(model)$topics
test_topic<-posterior(model,newdata=tdmtest)$topics
par(mfrow=c(1,2))
topic.image(train_topic,main='Training data ')
topic.image(test_topic,main='Testing data ')

corpus = Corpus(VectorSource(tweet$comments))
corpus = tm_map(corpus,removePunctuation)
corpus = tm_map(corpus,stripWhitespace)
corpus = tm_map(corpus,tolower)
tdm = DocumentTermMatrix(corpus)
term_tfidf <- tapply(tdm$v/row_sums(tdm)[tdm$i], tdm$j, mean) * log2(nDocs(tdm)/col_sums(tdm > 0))
summary(term_tfidf)
##    Min. 1st Qu.  Median    Mean 3rd Qu.    Max. 
##  0.1315  1.2532  1.5482  1.8237  1.9959 14.9710
tdm <- tdm[,term_tfidf >= 0.1]
tdm <- tdm[row_sums(tdm) > 0,]
k = 10;#number of topics
SEED = 786; # number of tweets used
CSC_TM <-list(VEM = LDA(tdmtrain, k = k, control = list(seed = SEED)),VEM_fixed = LDA(tdm, k = k,control = list(estimate.alpha = FALSE, seed = SEED)),Gibbs = LDA(tdm, k = k, method = "Gibbs",control = list(seed = SEED, burnin = 1000,thin = 100, iter = 1000)),CTM = CTM(tdm, k = k,control = list(seed = SEED,var = list(tol = 10^-4), em = list(tol = 10^-3))))

#####################################################################
save(CSC_TM,file="CSC_TM.rda")
